  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Establishment of the Assuring the Future of Forest with Integrated Risk Management (AFFIRM) Mechanism</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Develop the AFFIRM conceptual framework, including the role, mission, strategy, key components under 
the relevant international agendas such as NBS, SFM, SFDRR, the Paris Agreement on climate change, Biodiversity, and UN SDGs.
Develop a mid-to long term road map for the implementation of the IFDRM Mechanism, including the work plan as a multi-donor programme. The mid-to long term road map is planned to be presented at the Forest Fire Forum of the XV WFC to be held in May 2022 in Seoul.</narrative>
  </description>
